basetypes.math

Class LayeredMatrix

  • java.lang.Object
    • basetypes.math.LayeredMatrix
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Processable<Vector,LayeredMatrix>

    public class LayeredMatrix
extends java.lang.Object
implements Processable<Vector,LayeredMatrix>
    Tensor-like type designed to store color image information in floating point format. Is internally represented by an array of Matrices for each channel.
    Author:
    Tristan
